
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Yoga for All | Hindu Community Center of Greater Cincinnati</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Yoga for All - 12-week holistic healing course at Hindu Community Center of Greater Cincinnati." />

  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="favicon.ico">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="favicon-32x32.png">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="favicon-16x16.png">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="apple-touch-icon.png">

  <style>
    :root {
      --saffron: #c56a1a;
      --deep-saffron: #9b4211;
      --maroon: #6f1f12;
      --gold: #d9a441;
      --cream: #fff8ea;
      --soft-cream: #fffdf7;
      --text: #3c2418;
      --muted: #765746;
      --border: rgba(197, 106, 26, 0.22);
      --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(76, 39, 14, 0.12);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(217,164,65,.18), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(197,106,26,.16), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fffaf0 0%, #fffdf7 46%, #fff8ea 100%);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    a { color: inherit; }

    .page-wrap { overflow: hidden; }

    .site-header {
      background: rgba(255, 253, 247, .94);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(197,106,26,.18);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .nav {
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: stretch;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .brand img {
      width: 64px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .brand-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--maroon);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 58px 24px 38px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr;
      gap: 38px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      color: var(--deep-saffron);
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 18px 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(44px, 6vw, 78px);
      line-height: .98;
      color: var(--maroon);
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 2.4vw, 30px);
      color: var(--deep-saffron);
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .intro {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 0 26px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }


    .hero-panel {
      height: 100%;
      min-height: 430px;
      padding: 34px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.62);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(76,39,14,.08);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 48px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(111,31,18,.14);
    }

    .btn.primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--deep-saffron), var(--saffron));
      color: white;
    }

    .btn.secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      border-color: var(--border);
      color: var(--maroon);
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .detail-card {
      position: relative;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      height: 100%;
      min-height: 430px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .detail-card:after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(217,164,65,.28);
      border-radius: 22px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .detail-card h2 {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: 28px;
      color: var(--maroon);
    }

    .details-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .detail-item {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,248,234,.92), rgba(255,255,255,.88));
      border: 1px solid rgba(197,106,26,.14);
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .detail-label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      color: var(--deep-saffron);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .detail-value {
      display: block;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .section {
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 46px 24px;
    }

    .section-kicker {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--deep-saffron);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .section h2 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      color: var(--maroon);
      font-size: clamp(30px, 3.4vw, 44px);
      line-height: 1.08;
    }

    .section-lead {
      max-width: 850px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 26px;
    }

    .pill-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .pill-card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(76,39,14,.08);
    }

    .pill-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .pill-card h3 { margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--maroon); font-size: 22px; }
    .pill-card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); }

    .months {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .month-card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
      min-height: 100%;
      border-radius: 26px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.84);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(76,39,14,.09);
    }

    .month-head {
      padding: 24px 24px 22px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(111,31,18,.96), rgba(197,106,26,.9));
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .month-head .weeks {
      display: inline-flex;
      width: fit-content;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      opacity: .9;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .month-head h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.18;
    }

    .month-body {
      padding: 24px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .month-body h4 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: var(--deep-saffron);
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
    }

    .practice, .goals {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    ul {
      margin: 0 0 18px 20px;
      padding: 0;
    }

    li { margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--muted); }

    .goals {
      padding-top: 0;
      border-top: 0;
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(197,106,26,.18);
      padding-left: 24px;
    }

    .two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 22px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .info-box {
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.76);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(76,39,14,.08);
    }

    .info-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--maroon);
      font-size: 25px;
    }

    .info-box p { margin: 0 0 14px; color: var(--muted); }
    .info-box ul { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .join {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 34px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,253,247,.96), rgba(255,248,234,.96));
      color: var(--text);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .join h2 { color: var(--maroon); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .join p { max-width: 760px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0 0 20px; }
    .join .section-kicker { color: var(--deep-saffron) !important; }
    .join .btn { background: var(--maroon); color: #fff8ea; box-shadow: none; }

    footer {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff8ea;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--maroon), var(--deep-saffron));
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #fff8ea;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .zeffy-wrap {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 0;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255,248,234,.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(197,106,26,.18);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(76,39,14,.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .zeffy-inner {
      border-radius: 22px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255,248,234,.92);
      border: 0;
      min-height: 420px;
    }

    .zeffy-inner iframe,
    .zeffy-inner [data-zeffy-embed],
    .zeffy-inner [data-zeffy-embed-fallback] {
      background: rgba(255,248,234,.92) !important;
      border-radius: 22px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero, .pill-row, .two-col, .month-card, .month-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero { padding-top: 28px; }
      .nav { align-items: flex-start; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .detail-card, .hero-panel { padding: 24px; min-height: auto; }
      .goals { border-left: 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(197,106,26,.18); padding-left: 0; padding-top: 18px; }
    }
  
    /* Shared HCCGC header/footer styling to support header.html and footer.html partials */
    .site-header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      background: rgba(255, 249, 241, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .site-header .container,
    .site-footer .container {
      width: min(calc(100% - 32px), 1220px);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .site-header .nav,
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      min-height: 92px;
      padding: 12px 0;
    }

    .site-header .brand,
    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      min-width: 0;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    .brand-logo-wrap {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 8px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .brand-logo {
      width: 88px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 12px;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .brand-text h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.15;
      color: var(--maroon);
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .site-header nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 18px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .site-header nav a {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    .site-header nav a:hover {
      color: var(--deep-saffron);
    }

    .menu-toggle {
      display: none;
      border: 0;
      background: transparent;
      padding: 6px 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .menu-toggle .bar,
    .menu-toggle span {
      display: block;
      width: 26px;
      height: 2px;
      margin: 5px 0;
      background: currentColor;
      transition: transform 0.22s ease, opacity 0.22s ease;
    }

    .menu-toggle.is-open .bar:nth-child(1),
    .menu-toggle.is-open span:nth-child(1) {
      transform: translateY(7px) rotate(45deg);
    }

    .menu-toggle.is-open .bar:nth-child(2),
    .menu-toggle.is-open span:nth-child(2) {
      opacity: 0;
    }

    .menu-toggle.is-open .bar:nth-child(3),
    .menu-toggle.is-open span:nth-child(3) {
      transform: translateY(-7px) rotate(-45deg);
    }

    .site-footer {
      padding: 24px 0 44px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(255,249,241,0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    .site-footer .footer-top {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 8px 0 0;
    }

    .site-footer .footer-nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .site-footer .footer-nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .site-footer .footer-nav a {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .site-footer .footer-nav a:hover,
    .site-footer .footer-email a:hover {
      color: var(--deep-saffron);
    }

    .site-footer .footer-email {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .site-footer .footer-social {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      gap: 12px;
      min-width: 220px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .site-footer .footer-social-label {
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .site-footer .social-icons {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .site-footer .social-icon {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(93, 43, 14, 0.10);
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease;
    }

    .site-footer .social-icon:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(93, 43, 14, 0.16);
    }

    .site-footer .social-icon svg {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      display: block;
    }

    .site-footer .footer-note {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .site-footer .copyright-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1120px) {
      .site-footer .footer-top {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        justify-items: start;
      }

      .site-footer .footer-email,
      .site-footer .footer-social {
        text-align: left;
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .site-header .nav,
      .nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .brand-logo {
        width: 74px;
      }

      .site-header nav ul {
        justify-content: flex-start;
        gap: 14px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .site-header .nav,
      .nav {
        align-items: stretch;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .site-header .brand,
      .brand {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .menu-toggle {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 2px;
      }

      .site-header nav {
        display: none;
        width: 100%;
        background: rgba(255, 249, 241, 0.95);
        padding: 10px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .site-header nav.is-open {
        display: block;
      }

      .site-header nav ul {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        gap: 14px;
        padding-top: 4px;
        padding-left: 4px;
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-wrap">
    <div id="header-placeholder"></div>
<main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-panel">
          <h1>Yoga for All</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">3 Month Holistic Healing Course</p>
          <p class="intro">A structured 12-week journey designed to help participants reset the body, build strength and balance, and integrate mindful practices for long-term wellness.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn primary" href="#join">Register</a>
            <a class="btn secondary" href="#course">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="detail-card" aria-label="Workshop details">
          <h2>Workshop Details</h2>
          <div class="details-grid">
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="detail-label">Duration</span>
              <span class="detail-value">12 Weeks / 3 Months</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="detail-label">Level</span>
              <span class="detail-value">Beginner → Intermediate</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="detail-label">Approach</span>
              <span class="detail-value">Reset → Build → Integrate</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="section-kicker">About the course</div>
        <h2>Build wellness one mindful step at a time.</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">Yoga for All is a progressive holistic healing course focused on gentle movement, breathwork, meditation, strength, balance, and emotional well-being. The course is designed to support participants across different fitness levels while maintaining a calm, safe, and respectful practice environment.</p>

        <div class="pill-row">
          <div class="pill-card">
            <div class="pill-icon">🌱</div>
            <h3>Reset</h3>
            <p>Start with mobility, breathing, relaxation, and body awareness.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pill-card">
            <div class="pill-icon">🌿</div>
            <h3>Build</h3>
            <p>Develop strength, stability, balance, stamina, and metabolic support.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pill-card">
            <div class="pill-icon">🌸</div>
            <h3>Integrate</h3>
            <p>Bring together breath, movement, meditation, clarity, and recovery.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="course">
        <div class="section-kicker">Course details</div>
        <h2>12-week progressive wellness journey</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">The program moves gradually from foundation and nervous-system reset to strength, balance, and integrated holistic wellness.</p>

        <div class="months">
          <article class="month-card">
            <div class="month-head">
              <div class="weeks">Weeks 1–4</div>
              <h3>🌱 Foundation & Reset</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="month-body">
              <div class="practice">
              <h4>Practice Focus</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Sookshma Vyayam / joint rotations</li>
                <li>Basic asanas: Tadasana, Cat-Cow, Child’s Pose</li>
                <li>Slow, controlled movements with no forceful stretching</li>
                <li>Deep breathing and abdominal breathing</li>
                <li>Compulsory Shavasana and 5-minute breath awareness meditation</li>
                <li>Daily practice time: 20–30 minutes</li>
              </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="goals">
                <h4>Goals</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Reduce stress, improve sleep, and calm the nervous system</li>
                  <li>Improve joint mobility and reduce stiffness or pain</li>
                  <li>Build body awareness and a healthier daily rhythm</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="month-card">
            <div class="month-head">
              <div class="weeks">Weeks 5–8</div>
